      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chat Is The Control Plane\nThe center chat is where you define the\ntask, scope, and follow-up instructions. It\nis not the place where you approve each file\nedit.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-7bab90997e6e",
      "originalText": "Chat Is The Control Plane\nThe center chat is where you define the task, scope, and follow-up instructions. It is not the place where you approve each file edit.",
