      "locked": false,
      "text": "Iterate In The Same Thread\nIf Codex got part of the job right, keep the\nsame thread and give precise follow-up\ninstructions. Reusing the thread preserves\ncontext, comments, and discovered evidence.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
