      "text": "Local And Worktree\nThe app uses Git checkouts to\nseparate foreground work from\nbackground work.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 22.5,
      "containerId": "node-a8e9da15b744",
      "originalText": "Local And Worktree\nThe app uses Git checkouts to separate foreground work from background work.",
