      "text": "Worktree Is The Background\nA worktree is a second checkout for the same\nrepo so Codex can run parallel tasks without\ndisturbing your local checkout.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-00910b6349ae",
      "originalText": "Worktree Is The Background\nA worktree is a second checkout for the same repo so Codex can run parallel tasks without disturbing your local checkout.",
