      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CLI For Approval Modes\nIf you want stronger approval gates, the CLI\nis closer to that model. OpenAI's docs define\nAuto, Read-only, and Full Access modes, and\nRead-only will not edit or run commands until\nyou approve a plan.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-9bbd44a9bb87",
      "originalText": "CLI For Approval Modes\nIf you want stronger approval gates, the CLI is closer to that model. OpenAI's docs define Auto, Read-only, and Full Access modes, and Read-only will not edit or run commands until you approve a plan.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
        "node_id": "cli-approval-modes"
      }
    },
